Package com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.filter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IJSONMapFilterListener
    This interface can be implemented to be notified about JSONMap objects being filtered, indicating whether a given JSONMap object is either included or excluded by the current AbstractJSONMapFilter instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractJSONMapFilter
    This abstract implementation for IJSONMapPreProcessor allows for filtering JSONMap instances.
    JSONMapFilterCompareDate
    This JSONMapFilterSpEL implementation allows for filtering JSONMap instances by comparing the value for the configured JSON property path against a given Date, using the configured JSONMapFilterCompareDate.DateComparisonOperator.
    JSONMapFilterListenerLogger
    This class allows for logging messages regarding JSONMap objects that are either included or excluded by AbstractJSONMapFilter instances.
    JSONMapFilterListenerLogger.LogExpressionInput  
    JSONMapFilterRegEx
    This AbstractJSONMapFilter implementation allows for filtering JSONMap instances by evaluating the configured Pattern instances against the value for the corresponding JSON property path.
    JSONMapFilterSpEL
    This AbstractJSONMapFilter implementation evaluates the configured SpEL expression against a given JSONMap instance, and either includes or excludes (based on the configured MatchMode) this JSONMap instance from further processing based on the expression evaluation result.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AbstractJSONMapFilter.MatchMode  
    JSONMapFilterCompareDate.DateComparisonOperator  
    JSONMapFilterListenerLogger.LogLevel
